external_knowledge:
- "Garden larger than the average garden size" refers to properties with a lot area greater than the average lot area;
- "Diamonds of the market in terms of quality and condition" implies that the properties have an overall quality and condition rating greater than 5;
- "How do they sparkle in terms of their price tags" refers to ordering the properties by their listing prices in descending order.

- 'high-priced' refers to prices above the median price;
- 'homes' are residential properties;
- 'pool' indicates the property has a swimming pool;
- 'asking prices' are the listing prices of the properties.
